1️⃣ Install Dependencies
pip install psutil

2️⃣ Run Script
python system_health_monitor.py

3️⃣ Check Log File

After running, check:

cat system_health.log


You’ll see entries like:

[2025-10-22 10:35:00] CPU Usage: 25%
[2025-10-22 10:35:00] Memory Usage: 68%
[2025-10-22 10:35:00] Disk Usage: 45%
[2025-10-22 10:35:00] Running Processes: 212
--------------------------------------------------


If thresholds are exceeded:

ALERT: High CPU usage detected: 91%
